description:
Mechanisms exist to establish and document the context surrounding Artificial Intelligence (AI) and Autonomous Technologies (AAT), including:
(1) Intended purposes;
(2) Potentially beneficial uses;
(3) Context-specific laws and regulations;
(4) Norms and expectations; and
(5) Prospective settings in which the system(s) will be deployed.

